{"tid":343244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"注入脂肪增大陰莖，30歲仔魂斷手術枱","createTime":"2017-08-01T09:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T03:59:45.000Z","uid":29314,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b31d5bf1190760c4f1b1f29f87d48da1bbb92ee1","tid":343244,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:44:54.000Z","msg":"瑞典斯德哥爾摩一名30歲男子接受陰莖增長和增粗手術後，兩小時內意外死亡，是歷來首宗陰莖增粗手術後死亡病例。<br />\n<br />\n有關個案刊登在《法醫學雜誌》。這宗手術在斯德哥爾摩一間私人整容診所進行，外科醫生首先替男子完成下體增長手術，之後再進行增粗手術，其間醫生將男子肚皮抽出的脂肪注入其陰莖內，不料脂肪經靜脈走入肺部，造成肺栓塞和血管破裂，最終令他心臟停頓。"},{"pid":"2136839725cdbce61a467367b7602b92d8afd0b5","tid":343244,"uid":130320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8df32dc2817c1c41e66854079e878bc0470411","tid":343244,"uid":61903,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:56:28.000Z","msg":"齋睇 topic以為強國<br />\n估唔到瑞典都有呢啲野"},{"pid":"72e03b71a4ea50bab33f3437512017629ad8863d","tid":343244,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:00:13.000Z","msg":"撚大噢"},{"pid":"303a74dd4b5460a609dc5deb01ccd3b168ce863a","tid":343244,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:28:36.000Z","msg":"死撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b41154220a437b7739e6884feed44803f3043e","tid":343244,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6e091e22f6aee5f9c6a8eda94045d86ca248a2","tid":343244,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:35:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7fb1e65f84b3f7ab4f341c8eecb2fdd7fb42be","tid":343244,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:37:25.000Z","msg":"好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47909f898c5cfd9ee1e3ffbe761c03c7a0ddef1","tid":343244,"uid":29740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"手術成功,但人死了"},{"pid":"f5c0411f314f499061b44c7a68e29df3e3ee734c","tid":343244,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T13:56:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>注入脂肪增大陰莖 30歲仔魂斷手術枱</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170801/57020174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170801%2F57020174&d=zyqxBc1rL4iI1hgoV0o7wp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=6a49cf30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170801%2F57020174&h=6ea7d60e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170801/57020174</a></div><br />\n<br />\n瑞典斯德哥爾摩一名30歲男子接受陰莖增長和增粗手術後，兩小時內意外死亡，是歷來首宗陰莖增粗手術後死亡病例。<br />\n<br />\n有關個案刊登在《法醫學雜誌》。這宗手術在斯德哥爾摩一間私人整容診所進行，外科醫生首先替男子完成下體增長手術，之後再進行增粗手術，其間醫生將男子肚皮抽出的脂肪注入其陰莖內，不料脂肪經靜脈走入肺部，造成肺栓塞和血管破裂，最終令他心臟停頓。<br />\n<br />\n醫生立即為男子施心肺復蘇法但不成功，他兩小時後在手術枱上死亡。病人原本沒有心臟病，身體亦健康。陰莖增大手術一向被視為簡單安全的手術，每年有大約8.4萬名男子接受有關手術。研究指出，今次是首宗用自體脂肪移植到陰莖術後死亡個案，又指若陰莖增粗和增長手術同時進行，風險會增加。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約每日新聞》/menshealth網"},{"pid":"50ee5497d619ff89e6b6b749e5cdfd6657526484","tid":343244,"uid":131621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:19:16.000Z","msg":"估錯地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b492ed62d2b52db1e2b2e53d9219a86bb7e9507d","tid":343244,"uid":129111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:50:21.000Z","msg":"30歲仲係仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536861f2690c74cfd95db5018108fb632e228c11","tid":343244,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:52:25.000Z","msg":"陰莖增大手術一向被視為簡單安全的手術，每年有大約8.4萬名男子接受有關手術。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8e2326625ad64025344e37f6ac12b79c30f369","tid":343244,"uid":73054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>30歲仲係仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n65歲都傑青 30歲算得咩"}]}